All you need to know about Cosrx 0.1 Retinol cream & 0.5 Retinol oil before choosing which one is for you!! 

Things to keep in mind - 
1) Both these products are recommended for nighttime use only, as Retinol can increase sun sensitivity. 

2) Before using retinol, make sure your skin is hydrated enough. Use a hydrating serum like hyaluronic acid serum before applying retinol. 

3) Start with a lower concentration: To avoid severe side effects, start with a lower concentration of retinol. 

4) Retinol can make your skin dry, so use a hydrating moisturiser after after applying retinol. 

5) Retinol can make your skin more sensitive to sunlight, so use a broad spectrum sunscreen with SPF 50. 

6) Retinol shouldn’t be used with Vitamin C or AHAs, BHA’s because it can lead to over exfoliation & skin irritation.
